                "type": "observation",
                "content": "A defining moment in my life: Priya discovered that a popular protein supplement she had been recommending to colleagues at her pharma firm was linked to a contamination recall \u2014 a brand she had trusted based on marketing alone, not lab data. \u2014 This incident hardened her into a quality-first buyer who now demands verified certifications and ingredient transparency before purchasing any consumable product, regardless of brand reputation or price.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T07:11:04.944095Z"
