              },
              {
                "age_when": 24,
                "event": "After relocating alone to Bengaluru for his first full-time role, Arjun spent three weekends researching apartments before renting a small but well-built single-occupancy flat in Koramangala, paying 15% above his initial budget because he found cheaper options had persistent plumbing issues confirmed by online tenant reviews.",
                "lasting_impact": "This decision embedded a recurring quality-vs-budget tension in his spending decisions, where he consistently anchors on peer reviews and real user experiences rather than brand claims before committing money."
