            "when": "age 38",
            "event": "After eighteen months of spreadsheet-driven analysis comparing thirty-two properties across Bengaluru, Srinivas purchased a 3BHK in Jayanagar, negotiating directly with the builder and refusing to use a broker despite family pressure.",
