                "age_when": 26,
                "event": "Shortly after his son was born, Rohit discovered that a budget cooking oil brand he had been buying caused his wife recurring digestive issues, later traced to substandard refining processes by a consumer forum he researched obsessively.",
                "lasting_impact": "This hardwired a deep quality-over-price instinct in him \u2014 he now scrutinizes ingredient labels and brand reputations meticulously before any household purchase, even when it strains their monthly budget."
              },
              {
                "age_when": 24,
                "event": "When Rohit applied for a personal loan to fund a small electronics side venture, the bank rejected his application citing insufficient income stability, forcing him to abandon the plan and rely on family savings to cover an emergency that same month.",
                "lasting_impact": "The experience embedded a lasting aversion to financial risk \u2014 he now maintains a rigid household budget spreadsheet and avoids any expenditure that cannot be justified against a concrete, near-term need."
