              {
                "age_when": 28,
                "event": "Rohit's father was diagnosed with Type 2 diabetes during a routine check-up, prompting Rohit to briefly investigate dietary changes including keto and low-carb plans for the whole family before concluding the restrictions were impractical given their income and his wife's traditional cooking preferences.",
